-virtualenv, then install required modules?

Example Installation
--------------------

(for debug only)
llvm-src$ ``./configure --enable-debug-runtime --enable-debug-symbols \
                        --prefix=$HOME/opt/llvm-3.4/``
llvm-src$ ``REQUIRES_RTTI=1 make all install``

llvmpy$ LLVM_CONFIG_PATH=$HOME/opt/numba/bin/llvm-config python setup.py build

